%N A015080 Inverse of 1071st cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015080 Periodic with period length 1071. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015080 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015080/b015080.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015080 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1071.
%H A015080 <a href="/index/Rec#order_576">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 576.
%H A015080 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015080 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015080 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1071,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Apr 01 2026 *)
%o A015080 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1071)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
%K A015080 sign,easy,changed
%O A015080 0,1
%A A015080 _Simon Plouffe_
